= {{project_name_short}} News =
{{IntroLike|
There are several ways to receive {{project_name_short}} news.
}}

{{IconSet|h1|1}} '''Choose What to Follow'''

Users with limited time should follow at least '''Important News'''. Users who want more detail can follow '''All News'''. All News includes Important News.

{{IconSet|h1|2}} '''Choose How to Receive It'''

The same news can be received through different delivery methods, such as the forum website, RSS, e-mail, or Telegram.

{{IconSet|h1|3}} '''Do Not Rely on Social Media Only'''

Social media posts may be delayed, incomplete, or not posted to every platform. Do not rely on social media as the only source for important {{project_name_short}} news.

{{IconSet|h1|4}} '''Select deliver method.'''

{{Tab
|type=controller
|addToClass=info-box
|content=

{{Tab
|title= == Important News ==
|active=true
|content=
'''Important News''' is recommended for all users.

Only critical information is posted here, such as {{project_name_short}} security advisories and important stable {{project_name_short}} releases.

Users with limited time should follow at least this news source.

'''Forum'''

* [https://forums.{{project_clearnet}}/tags/important-news {{project_name_short}} Important News Forum Tag] ([http://forums.{{project_onion}}/tags/important-news onion])

'''RSS'''

* Clearnet: [https://forums.{{project_clearnet}}/tags/important-news.rss https://forums.{{project_clearnet}}/tags/important-news.rss] [[File:Feed-icon.jpeg|25px|alt={{project_name_short}} Important News Forum Tag RSS|link=https://forums.{{project_clearnet}}/tags/important-news.rss]]
* Onion: [http://forums.{{project_onion}}/tags/important-news.rss http://forums.{{project_onion}}/tags/important-news.rss] [[File:Feed-icon.jpeg|25px|alt={{project_name_short}} Important News Forum Tag Onion RSS|link=http://forums.{{project_onion}}/tags/important-news.rss]]

'''E-mail'''

Users who prefer e-mail can subscribe through the [https://forums.{{project_clearnet}} {{project_name_short}} Forums]. After registering, users can subscribe to the [https://forums.{{project_clearnet}}/tags/important-news {{project_name_short}} Important News Forum Tag].
}} <!-- close tab -->

{{Tab
|title= == All News ==
|content=
'''All News''' includes Important News plus general project updates.

This may include testing announcements, development news, new features, future plans, calls for testing, updated documentation, and other project news.

All News is useful for users who want to follow {{project_name_short}} development more closely.

'''Forum'''

* [https://forums.{{project_clearnet}}/c/news {{project_name_short}} News Forum] ([http://forums.{{project_onion}}/c/news onion])

'''RSS'''

* Clearnet: [https://forums.{{project_clearnet}}/c/news.rss https://forums.{{project_clearnet}}/c/news.rss] [[File:Feed-icon.jpeg|25px|alt={{project_name_short}} News Forum RSS|link=https://forums.{{project_clearnet}}/c/news.rss]]
* Onion: [http://forums.{{project_onion}}/c/news.rss http://forums.{{project_onion}}/c/news.rss] [[File:Feed-icon.jpeg|25px|alt={{project_name_short}} News Forum Onion RSS|link=http://forums.{{project_onion}}/c/news.rss]]

'''E-mail'''

Users who prefer e-mail can subscribe through the [https://forums.{{project_clearnet}} {{project_name_short}} Forums]. After registering, users can subscribe to the [https://forums.{{project_clearnet}}/c/news {{project_name_short}} News Forum].
}} <!-- close tab -->

{{Tab
|title= == Telegram ==
|content=
Telegram is another delivery method for news updates.

The Telegram News Channel provides {{project_name_short}} website <code>{{project_clearnet}}</code> server status updates and news updates.

[[File:1024px-Telegram_2019_Logo.svg.png|25px|link=https://t.me/s/{{project_telegram_all_news_channel_name}}]] {{ExtLink
|https://t.me/s/{{project_telegram_all_news_channel_name}}
|text={{project_name_short}} Telegram News Channel
|icons=none
}}

Do not rely on Telegram as the only source for important news.
}} <!-- close tab -->

{{Tab
|title= == Social Media ==
|content=
There are some [[Official Online Profiles|Official {{project_name_short}} Social Media Profiles]] online.

Do not rely on social media for the latest {{project_name_short}} news or for urgent security information. Social media posts may be delayed, incomplete, or not posted to every platform.

Some messages from the {{project_name_short}} Feature Blog are also posted on:

* [[File:1024px-Telegram_2019_Logo.svg.png|25px|link=https://t.me/s/{{project_name_short}}]] {{ExtLink
|https://t.me/s/{{project_name_short}}
|text={{project_name_short}} Telegram News Channel
|icons=none
}}
* [[File:twitter.png|25px|link=https://twitter.com/{{project_name_short}}]] {{ExtLink
|https://twitter.com/{{project_name_short}}
|text={{project_name_short}} Twitter Profile
|icons=none
}}
* [[File:facebook.png|25px|link=https://www.facebook.com/{{project_name_short}}]] {{ExtLink
